0Akasa%20Airlines%2C%20had%20clearly%20explained%20the%20roadmap%20to%20aviation%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20understand%20the%20field%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nazeeya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Class%2011%2C%20Samaira%20was%20sure%20she%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20pilot%2C%20however%2C%20an%20uncertainty%20persisted.%20%E2%80%9CA%20friend%20of%20mine%20said%20something%20that%20made%20me%20look%20at%20things%20differently%3A%20%E2%80%98How%20many%20parents%20tell%20their%20kids%20to%20become%20pilots%3F%20Consider%20yourself%20lucky%20and%20give%20it%20your%20best.%E2%80%99%20And%20there%20was%20no%20turning%20back%20from%20that%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20Samaira%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFlight%20license%20in%2018%20months%20of%20training%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20her%20Class%2012%20board%20exams%2C%20Samaira%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20and%20joined%20Vinod%20Yadav%20Aviation%20Academy.%20There%20were%20six%20papers%20in%20aviation%20%E2%80%93%20Air%20Regulation%2C%20Aviation%20Meteorology%2C%20Air%20Navigation%2C%20Technical%20General%2C%20Technical%20Specific%2C%20and%20Radio%20Telephony%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20one%20needs%20to%20secure%2070%20percent%20to%20clear%20the%20papers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20average%20student%20might%20take%20one%20or%20two%20attempts%20to%20clear%20the%20exams%2C%20Samaira%2C%20with%20her%20focus%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20passed%20all%20five%20papers%20in%20the%20first%20attempt.%20%E2%80%9CI%20spent%20my%20entire%20time%20in%20Delhi%20studying%20and%20giving%20my%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3