Fa%3E's%20political%20activities%20and%20the%20company's%20declining%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELehigh%20County%2C%20located%20toward%20the%20east%20of%20Pennsylvania%20with%20a%20relatively%20affluent%20population%20that%20is%20often%20a%20swing%20county%2C%20has%20a%20county%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epension%20board%20that%20oversees%20%24500%20million%20in%20assets.%20It%20is%20the%20first%20known%20US%20pension%20fund%20to%20stop%20purchasing%20new%20Tesla%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20Musk's%20choice%20to%20become%20a%20political%20figure%20rather%20than%20a%20customer-focused%20leader%20has%20compromised%20the%20Tesla%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Pinsley%2C%20the%20Lehigh%20County%20controller%20who%20first%20introduced%20a%20motion%20to%20cease%20Tesla%20investments%2C%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20with%20organizers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-takedown-protests-origin-story-history-elon-musk-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20Takedown%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla's%20earnings%20are%20down%2071%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20their%20auto%20revenues%20have%20dropped%2020%25%2C%20and%20profitability%20has%20taken%20a%20sharp%20dive%2C%26quot%3B%20Pinsley%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20owe%20it%20to%20our%20retirees%20and%20taxpayers%20to%20take%20a%20hard%20look%20at%20whether%20these%20are%20wise%20investments%20at%20this%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20board%20not%20only%20voted%20to%20hit%20the%20brakes%20on%20new%20Tesla%20investments%20in%20a%204-2%20decision%2C%20it%20has%20also%20and%20directed%20the%20county's%20investment%20manager%20to%20draft%20a%20report%20outlining%20options%20to%20divest%20its%20passively%20managed%20funds%20from%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lehigh%20County%20Controller's%20Office%20and%20Tesla%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPinsley%20and%20the%20retirement%20board%20of%20Lehigh%20County%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20concerned%20about%20pensions%20invested%20in%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20a%20group%20of%2051%20New%20York%20State%20legislators%20called%20on%20the%20state%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-role-damage-tesla-pension-stakeholders-state-treasurers-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edivest%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20%241%20billion%20in%20Tesla%20holdings.%20A%20top%20contender%20in%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Comptroller%20race%20has%20pledged%20to%20pull%20the%20city's%20%24300%20billion%20pension%20portfolio%20out%20of%20Tesla%20if%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrad%20Lander%2C%20the%20current%20New%20York%20City%20Comptroller%2C%20has%20also%20been%20vocal%20about%20his%20dissatisfaction%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-part-time-ceo-tesla-spacex-challenges-sales-drop-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMusk's%20leadership%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20stopped%20short%20of%20calling%20for%20a%20divestment%20in%20his%20office's%20latest%20response%20to%20BI%20in%20April.%20The%20city's%20five%20public%20pension%20systems%20held%20more%20than%203%20million%20Tesla%20shares%20worth%20about%20%241.26%20billion%20on%20December%2031%2C%202024%2C%20yet%20this%20figure%20has%20shrunk%20to%20%24831%20million%20by%20March%2028%2C%20according%20to%20the%20comptroller's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20eight%20state%20treasurers%20penned%20a%20joint%20letter%20to%20Tesla's%20board%20to%20express%20concern%20over%20Musk's%20lack%20of%20focus%20on%20Tesla%2C%20and%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Teachers%20is%20pressing%20major%20asset%20managers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20BlackRock%20and%20Vanguard%20%E2%80%94%20to%20consider%20divestment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20US%20border%2C%20the%20Netherlands'%20largest%20pension%20fund%20offloaded%20its%20%24600%20million%20stake%20in%20Tesla%20in%20January.%20Denmark's%20%2420%20billion%20pension%20fund%2C%20AkademikerPension%2C%20followed%20suit%20in%20March.%20Recently%2C%20Canada's%20largest%20public-sector%20union%20also%20urged%20national%20pension%20funds%20to%20cut%20ties%20with%20Tesla%2C%20though%20divestments%20have%20yet%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20been%20facing%20growing%20pressure%20over%20Musk's%20governance%20of%20the%20company%20and%20his%20political%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20Takedown%20movement%20that%20emerged%20in%20protest%20of%20Musk's%20involvement%20in%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20office%20is%20aiming%20to%20evolve%20beyond%20demonstrations.%20The%20movement's%20next%20goal%20is%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehelping%20cities%20and%20states%20develop%20resolutions%20to%20divest%20in%20%26quot%3Ball%20things%20Musk%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20on%20April%2022%20after%20Tesla%20reported%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20May%206%2C%20Tesla%20stock%20has%20declined%20more%20than%2027%25%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%202025%2C%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-earnings-call-report-tsla-stock-live-updates-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQ1%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%20missed%20expectations.%20Musk%20has%20announced%20during%20the%20latest%20earnings%20call%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-ceo-doge-white-house-tsla-stock-investors-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20will%20be%20stepping%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20his%20political%20activities%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarketing%20experts%20have%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20Tesla%20has%20alienated%20its%20core%20customer%20base%2C%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-sales-elon-musk-rebranding-saved-learning-from-airline-disasters-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22