C%20my%20understanding%20is%20you've%20got%20a%20six-pack%20of%20white%20women%2C'%26quot%3B%20Submaranian%20told%20Geragos%2C%20according%20to%20a%20court%20transcript%20of%20the%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BLike%20that's%20not%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20something%20that%20you%20shouldn't%20%E2%80%94%20that%20no%20one%20should%20be%20saying%20as%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20Court%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20bar%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeragos%20%E2%80%94%20a%20criminal%20defense%20attorney%20who%20has%20represented%20Michael%20Jackson%20and%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20among%20other%20boldfaced%20names%20%E2%80%94%20spoke%20about%20the%20Combs%20case%20on%20a%20Friday%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3B2%20Angry%20Men%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20podcast%20he%20co-hosts%20with%20TMZ%20founder%20Harvey%20Levin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20describing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20six-pack%20of%20white%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20Geragos%20said%20the%20prosecutors%20mischaracterized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcassie-ventura-breaks-silence-on-sean-diddy-combs-assault-video-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20surveillance%20video%20where%20Combs%20beat%20his%20former%20partner%20Cassie%20Ventura%20in%20a%20hotel%20hallway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20Combs%20was%20upset%20because%20she%20took%20her%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20you%20ever%20had%20a%20situation%20where%20your%20significant%20other%20took%20your%20cellphone%3F%26quot%3B%20Geragos%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20does%20that%20take%20you%20from%200%20to%2060%20really%20quick%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubmaranian%20admonished%20Geragos%20for%20the%20comments%20about%20the%20prosecutors%2C%20saying%20he%20violated%20a%20court%20rule%20barring%20lawyers%20involved%20in%20ongoing%20cases%20from%20making%20%26quot%3Bextrajudicial%20comments%26quot%3B%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20marks%20a%20rough%20start%20for%20the%20legal%20team%20in%20Combs'%2