s%20over%2055%20million%20customers%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20insurer%20built%20an%20AI%20tool%20into%20its%20agents'%20workflow%20to%20increase%20customer%20loyalty.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fbuild-it-connectivity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuild%20IT%3A%20Connectivity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20about%20tech%20powering%20better%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20insurance%20agents%2C%20quick%20access%20to%20policy%20data%20is%20essential%20to%20helping%20customers%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%2055%20million%20customers%20around%20the%20world%2C%20Zurich%20Insurance%20Group%20relies%20on%20strong%20customer%20relationships%20to%20stay%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInteraction%20is%20by%20far%20the%20biggest%20driver%20of%20loyalty%20with%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Aleksandar%20Vidovi%C4%87%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Zurich's%20AI%20and%20analytics%20company%2C%20ZCAM%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZurich%20has%20a%20network%20of%20thousands%20of%20agents%20worldwide%20who%20work%20directly%20with%20customers.%20Their%20main%20job%20is%20selling%20insurance%20policies%2C%20but%20the%20role%20also%20involves%20explaining%20complicated%20policy%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20communicate%20across%20various%20channels%2C%20including%20phone%20calls%2C%20emails%2C%20and%20WhatsApp%20messages.%20The%20agents%20told%20Vidovi%C4%87's%20team%20that%20juggling%20these%20channels%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ploughing%20through%20dense%20policy%20documents%2C%20could%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20details%20needed%20to%20give%20each%20customer%20a%20tailored%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Vidovi%C4%87%20said%20that%20the%20agents%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20trying%20to%20determine%20whether%20customers%20were%20covered%20for%20a%20specific%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20imagine%20going%20through%2010%20or%2015%20pages%20of%20insurance%20jargon.%20It%20can%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20data%20on%20customers%20and%20company%20policies%20was%20scattered%20across%20systems%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20not%20provided%20to%20the%20agents%20at%20all.%20In%20January%202024%2C%20Vidovi%C4%87's%20team%20set%20about%20creating%20a%20customer%20relationship%20management%20system%20that%20could%20connect%20the%20dispersed%20datasets%20to%20help%20the%20agents%20give%20every%20customer%20what%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296ef0a39-bc71-44d7-b4cb-5b4a8f6077e0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimplifying%20customer%20support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20team's%20guiding%20design%20principles%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bthree-click%20rule%26quot%3B%3A%20No%20agent%20should%20need%20more%20than%20three%20clicks%20to%20get%20what%20they%20need.%20Whether%20it%20was%20pulling%20up%20a%20customer's%20policy%20details%20or%20sending%20a%20follow-up%20message%2C%20everything%20had%20to%20be%20fast%20and%20intuitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZurich%2C%20which%20serves%20customers%20in%20more%20than%20215%20countries%20and%20territories%2C%20is%20familiar%20with%20rolling%20out%20new%20technology%3B%20it%20has%20implemented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.postonline.co.uk%2Ftechnology%2F7955251%2Fzurich-reveals-it-has-found-more-than-160-use-cases-for-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20160%20AI-powered%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20its%20operations.%20But%20when%20it%20came%20to%20developing%20a%20new%20approach%20to%20the%20CRM%2C%20there%20wasn't%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20solution%20because%20different%20agents%20use%20different%20platforms.%20To%20tackle%20this%2C%20it%20built%20the%20CRM's%20interface%20into%20existing%20tools%20like%20Microsoft%20Outlook%20and%20Salesforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20part%20of%20the%20solution%20involved%20putting%20customer%20and%20policy%20data%20into%20one%20easy-to-navigate%20platform.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20speaking%20with%20a%20customer%2C%20the%20intelligence%20platform%20allows%20an%20agent%20to%20easily%20find%20their%20current%20policies%20and%20records%20of%20previous%20interactions.%20This%20data%20then%20connects%20to%20AI%20features%20within%20other%20platforms%2C%20such%20as%20tone%20analysis%20and%20messaging%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CRM%20also%20helps%20each%20agent%20suggest%20the%20customer's%20next%20steps%2C%20with%20the%20company%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20tech%20giants%20like%20Spotify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20listen%20to%20Spotify%2C%20we%20get%20a%20playlist%20and%20then%20it%20recommends%20the%20next%20best%20song%2C%26quot%3B%20Vidovi%C4%87%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20use%20the%20same%20modeling%20to%20recognize%20the%20most%20appropriate%20product%20for%20a%20customer%20based%20on%20their%20needs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20CRM%20is%20now%20used%20in%20four%20of%20the%20company's%20markets%20in%20Zurich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20customer%20interaction%20because%20it%20takes%20less%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Vidovi%C4%87%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20agents%20don't%20need%20to%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20drafting%20up%20specific%20messages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Zurich's%20initial%20calculations%2C%20the%20team%20could%20cut%20servicing%20times%20by%20over%2070%25%2C%20though%20Vidovi%C4%87%20said%20that%20they%20hope%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20tool's%20impact%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6a6a848-b3bc-43fa-90cd-cecfbdb07739%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransforming%20the%20insurance%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Poux%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20risk%20management%20at%20th