ch%20tariffs%20are%20raising%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20White%20House%20torched%20Amazon%20when%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20the%20online%20retailer%20was%20considering%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%20later%20denied%20that%20it%20was%20ever%20going%20to%20display%20the%20cost%20of%20tariffs%20next%20to%20each%20item.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%20want%20to%20know%20how%20much%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20trade%20war%20is%20raising%20the%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20lambasted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-bezos-removed-tariff-info-amazon-listings-after-call-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20the%20online%20retailer%20might%20display%20the%20cost%20of%20tariffs%20next%20to%20individual%20products.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-reported-amazon-tariff-price-plan-hostile-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20later%20denied%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20news%20report%2C%20but%20a%20firestorm%20had%20already%20begun.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20hostile%20and%20political%20act%20by%20Amazon%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20said%20in%20response%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20Economist%2FYouGov%20poll%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20Americans%20want%20that%20very%20type%20of%20price%20transparency.%20The%20poll%20found%20that%2061%25%20of%20US%20adults%20agree%20that%20businesses%20%26quot%3Bshould%20display%20how%20much%20of%20a%20purchase%20price%20goes%20toward%20paying%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroken%20down%2C%2080%25%20of%20Democrats%2C%2061%25%20of%20independents%2C%20and%2042%25%20of%20Republicans%20agreed%20that%20businesses%20should%20display%20tariff%20price%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20major%20companies%2C%20including%20Walmart%2C%20Mattel%2C%20Conagra%2C%20and%20Best%20Buy%2C%20have%20said%20they%20could%20raise%20prices%20in%20response%20to%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs.%20Economists%20expect%20that%20cars%2C%20food%2C%20toys%2C%20and%20other%20goods%20will%20become%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20Trump%20and%20the%20White%20House%20have%20said%20that%20temporary%20price%20increases%20are%20part%20of%20the%20necessary%20pain%20needed%20for%20a%20trade%20policy%20that%20returns%20more%20manufacturing%20to%20the%20US.%20The%20president%20has%20said%20that%20children%20have%20too%20many%20toys%20and%20should%20be%20content%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-what-china-exports-besides-toys-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Btwo%20dolls%20instead%20of%2030%20dolls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20said%20the%20US%20is%20nearing%20trade%20agreements%20with%20some%20countries.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20testified%20to%20Congress%20that%20talks%20haven't%20even%20begun%20with%20China.%20The%20US%20is%20imposing%20a%20145%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20goods.%20Beijing%20has%20said%20it%20would%20welcome%20discussions%20but%20is%20also%20prepared%20to%20stomach%20a%20lengthy%20trade%20war%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Trump's%20approval%20rating%20has%20taken%20a%20significant%20hit.%20Polls%20also%20show%20that%20Americans%20have%20also%20soured%20on%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Economist-YouGov%20poll%20found%20Trump%20has%20a%20-10%20percentage%20point%20net%20approval%2C%20which%20is%20higher%20than%20Nate%20Silver's%20weighted%20average%20(-7.3)%20and%20RealClearPolitics'%20average%20(-5.9).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20political%20situation%20doesn't%20improve%2C%20Republicans%20coul