-indian-mountaineering-adventhrill-dehradun%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20in%20banking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20working%20your%20way%20up%20to%20the%20position%20of%20Vice%20President%20at%20Credit%20Suisse%2C%20but%20feeling%20that%20something%20was%20still%20missing.%20That%20was%20the%2039-year-old%20banker%E2%80%99s%20dilemma.%20While%20he%20had%20everything%20many%20would%20envy%2C%20there%20was%20one%20thing%20that%20tugged%20at%20his%20heart%20%E2%80%94%20his%20undying%20craving%20for%20the%20authentic%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spiced%20chickpeas%20served%20with%20soft%20leavened%20flatbread)%20he%20grew%20up%20eating%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Sagar%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20secure%20career%20to%20pursue%20a%20project%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20entirely%20sure%20about.%20Motivated%20by%20his%20love%20for%20food%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20turn%20his%20passion%20into%20a%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20started%20with%20my%20desire%20to%20bring%20the%20authentic%20taste%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20That%20one%20thought%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first-ever%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BHome%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22